column2: SELECT COUNT(a0),  COUNT(a1),  COUNT(a2) FROM (SELECT  CASE WHEN ra BETWEEN # AND # AND dec BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END a0,  CASE WHEN ra BETWEEN # AND # AND dec BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END a1,  CASE WHEN ra BETWEEN # AND # AND dec BETWEEN # AND # THEN # END a3  FROM PhotoObj ) PhotoObj
